title: VELVET # 001
description:
Centering on the mysterious Velvet Templeton, a seemingly mild-mannered secretary who harbors an intense, espionage-laden past, Velvet sees longtime Captain America collaborators Ed Brubaker and Steve Epting reuniting for another tale of international intrigue, murder and over the top action.

BY ED BRUBAKER AND STEVE EPTING

PUBLISHED BY IMAGE COMICS

ENJOY AND SEED...
